comments: Jones (NOP) legally contests Siakam's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Valanciunas (NOP) clamps and holds Poeltl's (TOR) left arm, affecting his ability to pursue the rebound.
Anunoby (TOR) legally contests Ingram's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Poeltl (TOR) establishes himself in Richardson's (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs as he rolls towards the basket.
Valanciunas (NOP) places his hand momentarily on Poeltl's (TOR) side before he immediately removes his hand.
Valanciunas (NOP) is moving alongside Barnes' (TOR) path and absorbs the contact from Barnes as he is passing the ball.
Poeltl (TOR) brings his hands forward towards the ball and marginal contact occurs with Jones (NOP) as they pursue the loose ball.
Jones (NOP) applies his forearm to SIakam's (TOR) upper body and he immediately removes his forearm as Siakam begins his upward shooting motion.
Correctly called 24 second violation.
Valanciunas (NOP) is already in Anunoby's (TOR) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Poeltl (TOR) does not maintain legal guarding position and initiates contact with Valanciunas' (NOP) arm during the rip-through.
Ingram (NOP) and Anunoby (TOR) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Valanciunas (NOP) slightly extends as he firms up over his right leg, and the contact with Anunoby's (TOR) side is marginal.
Anunoby (TOR) legally contests Ingram's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Poeltl (TOR) is already in Jones' (NOP) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Valanciunas (NOP) is late to the spot, and does not maintain verticality, and initiates contact with Siakam (TOR) during his driving shot attempt.
McCollum (NOP) briefly grasps Poeltl's (TOR) jersey during rebounding.
Ingram (NOP) brings his arm down and makes contact with Poeltl's (TOR) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Valanciunas (NOP) is already in Anunoby's (TOR) path and is firming up over his left leg when contact occurs.

McCollum (NOP) briefly grasps and immediately releases Trent Jr.'s (TOR) arm as he moves to set the pick.

Siakam (TOR) goes to not through Jones' (NOP) space and marginal contact occurs as he passes the ball.
McCollum (NOP) legally contests Trent Jr.'s (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Anunoby (TOR) brings his hand towards Ingram's (NOP) front and marginal contact occurs off ball during the inbound.
Ingram (NOP) brings his hands towards Trent Jr. (TOR) and marginal contact occurs as Ingram releases away to receive the pass.
Anunoby (TOR) legally contests Ingram's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Jones (NOP) brings his forearm towards SIakam's (TOR) side and marginal contact occurs in the backcourt.
Jones (NOP) moves slightly forward towards Siakam (TOR) and marginal contact occurs in the backcourt.
Siakam (TOR) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot and he legally lifts his pivot foot to pass the ball.
As Siakam (TOR) gains possession, his momentum legally carries him into the backcourt.
